                    "3. Λ⁰ has quark content uds → S = −1",
                    "4. π⁰ has quark content (uū−dd̄)/√2 → S = 0",
                    "5. Initial S = −1 + 0 = −1; Final S = −1 + 0 = −1 ✓",
                    "6. Strangeness conserved → this is a strong interaction (fast reaction)"
