                    "y₁ = A sin(kx − ωt) carries intensity I = +½ρvω²A² (rightward)",
                    "y₂ = A sin(kx + ωt) carries intensity I = −½ρvω²A² (leftward)",
                    "Net intensity = 0 → no net energy transfer",
                    "However, the total energy ∫½ρω²(2A sin kx)² dx = ρω²A²L is non-zero — energy is stored."
